data.description: Welcome to your dream home in sunny Hemet, Riverside County! This charming property, nestled on a generously sized lot of 6,970 square feet, stands out among its peers in the area. Built in 1989, this well-maintained home boasts a comfortable and efficient layout with 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, spanning approximately 1200 square feet. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by a turnkey residence in pristine move-in condition. The property exudes a sense of timeless appeal, showcasing the care and attention to detail that has gone into its maintenance. The spacious living areas are adorned with tasteful tile flooring, creating a clean and inviting atmosphere throughout. The kitchen is not only functional but also stylish, with various upgrades enhancing its aesthetic appeal. The property offers a bonus room for storage within the garage, catering to your organizational needs. The well-designed layout extends to the backyard, where a concrete patio ensures easy maintenance and provides an ideal space for outdoor gatherings.    Hemet, with its roots traced back to the growth stimulated by Lake Hemet, offers a vibrant community surrounded by picturesque parks. This property, with its advantageous location, provides residents with easy access to the natural beauty and recreational opportunities that abound in the area.    Don't miss the chance to make this delightful property your new home. Contact us today to schedule an appointment and explore firsthand the unique charm and value this home brings to the market. Your sunny Hemet oasis awaits!
